  "text": "We now go through the relevant assumptions necessary to apply Theorem 1 to the recommendation systems context. As mentioned above, these are the same assumptions as those in [CITATION_1] : an exposition of these assumptions is also given there. Then, we prove Theorem 2, which shows that Algorithm 3 gives the same guarantees on recommendations as the quantum algorithm.",
